# Database Reset Policy

The project is currently in first-version development.

- Do not create or maintain database migrations unless the user explicitly asks for them.
- Prefer recreating the database schema from scratch when database structure changes are needed.
- It is acceptable to drop and rebuild development data during this phase, after confirming any destructive action with the user when it affects an existing local or remote database.
